social_posts.post_text:
Humpback whale and her calf 🐋 
•
Trip made. AMAZING how tiny that is compared to this humongous Humpback! Humpbacks typically max out around 50ft long, and I believe this specimen was every bit of that...if not more. Came to Cabo wanting to capture this, so stoked 🥺🤙🏼
